- [ ] OCR processing completes and stores structured OCR results; OCR status transitions through pending -> in_progress -> completed.
- [ ] Manual correction UI enables editing of OCR text; corrections are saved as new file version with revision history.
- [ ] Metadata indexing supports search by filename, OCR text, tags, owner, and related study; search results are accurate and fast.
- [ ] Access control works: only owner or shared users can view/download/edit; unauthorized access is denied with clear errors.
- [ ] All frontend arrays and API responses guarded for null/undefined values as per runtime safety rules.
- [ ] Page_p006, page_p007, and page_p008 integrate seamlessly with the feature, with consistent design system usage and responsive behavior.

